-- China May Ask Banks for Daily Monitoring of Loans, Business News Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-01T23:53:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/china-may-ask-banks-for-daily-monitoring-of-loans-business-news-reports.html
China may ask banks to record average
daily balances for loans and deposits instead of compiling
figures at the end of the month, China Business News reported
today, citing an unidentified person.  The change aims at better liquidity management, the report
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
